    <item>
      <title>瑞士冷冻俄罗斯资产塔利跃升至84亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/swiss-froze-28-more-russian-assets-in-past-year-following-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士当局冻结的俄罗斯资产价值跃升至74亿瑞士法郎（84亿美元），因为该国对数百名被视为接近克里姆林宫的俄罗斯个人和公司采取了进一步的欧洲联盟的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/swiss-froze-28-more-russian-assets-in-past-year-following-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 07:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金牌记录是特朗普的贸易威胁粉丝避风港的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/gold-xauusd-hits-fresh-record-as-trump-s-looming-levies-boost-havens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戈德在新季度开始时创下了记录，这是美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在本周应得的贸易关税的重大升级，这加剧了人们对全球经济和扇形避风港需求的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/gold-xauusd-hits-fresh-record-as-trump-s-looming-levies-boost-havens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 06:16:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>碰碰运气在随着交易者等待特朗普举动的交易者而稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统回到对俄罗斯的评论后，石油稳定了，这引发了自1月以来最大的价格上涨，而市场却归功于关税的到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:26:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Trafigura同意在巴西案件中支付7600万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trafigura-agrees-to-pay-brazil-49-million-over-bribery-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特拉菲格拉集团（Trafigura Group）同意支付7580万美元，以解决巴西的案件，此前该案件去年承认支付贿赂以赢得全国的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trafigura-agrees-to-pay-brazil-49-million-over-bribery-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:46:57 GMT</pubDate>
